                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5469" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0821</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7970 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">触目惊心的业绩翻转——航天通信母子公司巨额前期差错更正</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shocking Performance Reversal ——Correction of Huge Prior Period Errors in Parent and Subsidiary Companies of Aerospace Communications</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许楠，张立娟，孙伟凡，李祎</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">航天通信控股集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">前期差错；差错更正；追溯重述；主动退市</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Prior period error; Error correction; Retrospective restatement;  Active delisting</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">*ST航通（原名航天通信）作为退市新规实施以来的首家主动退市企业备受关注，其母子公司巨额前期差错更正造成的业绩翻转是导致其退市的直接原因。航天通信直至2019年末才发现其原控股子公司智慧海派自2016年纳入合并范围之后发生的舞弊行为，因此智慧海派和航天通信分别针对前期差错进行了更正。智慧海派通过调减虚增的巨额收入与利润、补提应收账款坏账准备、全额计提存货跌价准备三个方面更正前期差错；航天通信一方面根据智慧海派更正的项目进行相应调整，另一方面将个别报表中关于智慧海派的长期股权投资以及合并报表中的商誉全额计提减值的时点确定为2016年，后又调整到2019年。同时，智慧海派和航天通信均重述了公司财务报表，合并报表2016年至2018年三年累计调低净利润近47亿元。本案例讲述了智慧海派和航天通信进行巨额前期差错更正的全过程，旨在引导学生由浅入深学习前期差错的定义、分类、更正方法及其对财务报表的影响，并思考母公司如何有效降低子公司引发重大前期差错更正的可能性。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> *ST Hangtong (formerly known as Aerospace Communications) has attracted much attention, as the first active delisting enterprise since the implementation of the new delisting rules. The direct reason for its delisting is the turnover of performance caused by the correction of huge errors in the previous period. Aerospace Communications didn&#39;t discover the fraud of its holding subsidiary until the end of 2019 after it was incorporated into the scope of merger in 2016, therefore both Smart Hipad and Aerospace Communications corrected the previous errors. Smart Hipad corrected the previous errors by reducing the huge amount of income and profit, making up the bad debt provision for accounts receivable and making full provision for inventory depreciation. One the one hand, Aerospace Communications made corresponding adjustments according to the corrected items of Smart, on the other hand, the time point of full provision for impairment of long-term equity investment in individual statements and goodwill in consolidated statements as 2016, and then it adjusted to 2019. At the same time, both Smart Hipad and Aerospace Communications restated the company’s financial statements, and the cumulated net profit of the consolidated statements in three years from 2016 to 2018 was reduced by nearly 4.7 billion yuan. This case describes the whole process of correcting huge errors in the early stage of Smart Hipad and Aerospace Communications. The purpose of this case is to guide students to learn the definition, classification, accounting treatment method of early-stage errors and their impact on financial statements from the shallower to the deeper, and to think about how the parent company can effectively reduce the possibility of major early-stage error correction caused by subsidiaries.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计理论与实务》、《会计学》、《中级财务会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">差错更正</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
